Package: SMLM
Type: Package
Title: Tools for clustering and topoligical data analysis of single molecule localization microscopy (SMLM) datasets. 
Version: 1.0
Date: 2018-05-16
Author: Jeremy Pike	
Maintainer: Jeremy Pike <j.a.pike@bham.ac.uk>
Description: Implements ToMaTo, DBCAN, Ripley K and Voronoi tesselation based cluster analysis. Persientent homology is also implented through TDA and the GHUDI library. Wrapper for C++ implentation of Topological Mode Analysis Tool (ToMaTo) clustering (https://geometrica.saclay.inria.fr/data/Steve.Oudot/clustering/). Makes use of ANN (A Library forApproximate Nearest Neighbor Searching). Is included.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Imports: Rcpp (>= 0.12.16)
LinkingTo: Rcpp
